notes: Rain stopped for 80 minutes with South Africa 164/2 (Boje 84*, Kallis 2*; 33 overs). Play resumed with no reduction in overs available to both sides.

stories.title: No illusions over difficulty of SA series
stories.summary: Going one down in our one-day series with South Africa is obviously disappointing, especially off the back of our recent success in Kenya

stories.title: Rain brings premature end to first one-day international
stories.summary: Torrential rain 38 overs into the South African innings drove the players from the field and brought a premature end to the first Standard Bank one-day international at the North West stadium in Potchefstroom on Friday

stories.title: 1st Match, South Africa v New Zealand, Statistical Highlights
stories.summary: It was the 1641st ODI in cricket history
